para_trans: Government Decision No: Grade - 2024 / Q. No.284 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Hospitals (State Level) Mumbai: Go by No. / Room 3 / T-2 / No. No.2476 / Category / Terkheda / Prasama / 15210-13/24, dated 13.08.2024.
Preface: - Terkheda (d. 100 bedded sub-district of Primary Health Centre at Vashi, District Dharashiv)
The matter of upgrading the hospital was under the consideration of the government. In this regard, the following decisions have been taken:
Government Decision: - Terkheda (d. 100 as a "special case" of the Primary Health Centre at Vashi, District Dharashiv).
Upgradation of the bedded sub-district hospital is being approved.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
